name: Main Door Rustic Mahogany V-Groove Arch-Top Slab Exterior Door
description: The SH-914 from Main Door combines Old World craftsmanship with state-of-the-art wood working. Prefinished and distressed, this solid wood 2-panel v-groove arch-top door provides charm and style to your existing frame. This 100% FSC certified door is ready to install.Please note: This is a slab door only, it is NOT A PREHUNG UNIT with a frame/jambs, it's application is to be hung onto your existing frame/jambsRustic clavos(decorative nails) and operational speakeasy with wrought-iron grill add to the charm and uniquenessGenuine mahogany type adds elegance and curb appeal to your homeSolid wood construction no veneersFSC certified ensures that product comes from responsibly managed forests
